Supplements for Athletic Performance

Creatine

• Dose: 5 g per day
• Post-Workout: Take 5 g after your gym workout with a meal that includes both carbs and protein (ideally with protein shake).
• Note: Be sure to drink plenty of water when taking creatine to avoid any stomach discomfort.

Magnesium

• Magnesium Bisglycinate:

This form is easily absorbed and gentle on the stomach. It also helps with muscle relaxation and improving sleep quality.

Best for: Intense training periods and supporting nighttime recovery.

• Magnesium Malate:

Great for energy production (via the Krebs cycle). It helps reduce feelings of fatigue and chronic tiredness.

Best for: Athletes who feel consistently drained or need an energy boost.

• Daily Dose for Athletes: 300-400 mg of magnesium per day.

